11 (6) The department shall adopt rules to implement this section, including rules that:
12 (a) Require an animal rescue entity to maintain a record for each animal in the legal
13 custody of the animal rescue entity;
14 (b) Establish a process for auditing animal rescue entities that incorporates consider-
